A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Mrs. Valarie Wilson on her outstanding public service as the
2 Executive Director of the Georgia School Boards Association; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Mrs. Valarie Wilson has long been recognized by the citizens of this state for
4 the vital role that she has played in leadership and her deep personal commitment to the
5 welfare of the citizens of Georgia; and
6 WHEREAS, she has diligently and conscientiously devoted innumerable hours of her time,
7 talents, and energy toward the betterment of her community and state as evidenced
8 dramatically by her superlative service with the Georgia School Boards Association and the
9 Board of City Schools of Decatur; and
10 WHEREAS, Mrs. Wilson served on Board of City Schools of Decatur from 2002-2011,
11 where she resiliently led the district through financial recession and was instrumental in the
12 establishment of the College Heights Early Childhood Learning Center; and
13 WHEREAS, Mrs. Wilson joined the Georgia School Boards Association in 2009, and
14 honorably served as its president from 2012 to 2013; and
